Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.storehouse.app.user.model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    @Entity
public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A user can either be a customer or employee. Employee can be either a administrator or just employee. Administrator must be set directly into the database. (not through the Java API here)
